</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  For the sins we have committed openly and in secret, (*)
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through imprudence,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through omission and laziness,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through ignorance,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     with premeditation and malice,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     using violence,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     letting ourselves be ruled by our base passions,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     despising our parents and teachers,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     in our work,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     wanting to be first,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through avarice,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through pride and arrogance,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     insulting our neighbour, (**)
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     by lying,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     speaking evil of others,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     slandering our neighbour,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through sexuality,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     looking lustfully,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through envy,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     through gluttony,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     being irresponsible,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     sowing discord,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     complaining in our heart,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     saddening the Holy Spirit,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">     "        "   "  "       "     resisting the will of God, (**)
</PRE></H3>

<H4><FONT COLOR="#000000">(*) After every verse the Assembly responds: Have mercy on us, for we are sinners!</FONT></H4>
